This is a brand page for the GLASSMAN WEALTH SERVICES trademark by Glassman Wealth Services, LLC 
                                in McLean, VA, 22182.
Write a review about a product or service associated with this GLASSMAN WEALTH SERVICES trademark.    
                                Or, contact the owner Glassman Wealth Services, LLC of the GLASSMAN WEALTH SERVICES trademark by filing a request to communicate with    
                                the Legal Correspondent for licensing, use, and/or questions related to the GLASSMAN WEALTH SERVICES trademark.
                           






On Tuesday, September 22, 2009,  a U.S. federal trademark registration was filed for 
                        GLASSMAN WEALTH SERVICES by 
                        Glassman Wealth Services, LLC, McLean, VA  22182.
                        The USPTO has given the GLASSMAN WEALTH SERVICES 
                        trademark serial  number of  77832111.  
                        The current federal status of this trademark filing is CONTINUED USE AND INCONTESTIBILITY ACCEPTED.
                        The correspondent listed for GLASSMAN WEALTH SERVICES is 
                        
                        
                                            Jacqueline L. Patt of 
                                            Markery Law LLC,  P.O. Box 84150, Gaithersburg MD 20883-4150 
                                .
                            The GLASSMAN WEALTH SERVICES trademark is filed in the category of 
                            
                                    Insurance & Financial Services
                                . 
                            The description provided to the USPTO for GLASSMAN WEALTH SERVICES 
                            is Financial planning and investment management. 
                            





