	IncFact analyzed data from the last recession to determine whether Glassman Wealth Services grew or shrank over that period. We also looked at other companies in the industry
	 to compare how recession-proof Glassman Wealth Services is relative to the industry. While a new recession may strike a particular industry, measuring the
	 industry and company's robustness during the last recession estimates its ability to weather future recessions.

	
