Giving Back















A community rich in hope is wealthy beyond measure.
We know true wealth is counted in more than dollars and cents. That’s why we’re as passionate about making a difference in our community as we are about creating wealth, opportunity, and security for our clients. Wherever we feel a personal connection to the issues, and wherever help is needed most, we are ready to lend a hand.
 
 
 














 
 
 







Chef Night

Our flagship charity event, Chef Night, has raised hundreds of thousands of dollars towards advancing a cure for brain tumors. Conceived by Barry Glassman, president of Glassman Wealth Services, Chef Night pairs an extravagant tasting menu with some of the best wines from around the world. All proceeds go to the National Brain Tumor Society for research grants and patient support programs.





 
 
 














 
 
 




