Glassman Wealth Services is proud and honored to be a sponsor of the Newsbabes Bash for Breast Cancer. An unprecedented event, the Newsbabes Bash for Breast Cancer unites anchorwomen from every major news network in the D.C. metropolitan area to shine a collective light on breast cancer causes. Click HERE for more information.
 
 
 










 
 
 














 
 
 




American Odyssey Relay
Glassman Wealth Services is proud to be a sponsor of the American Odyssey Relay, a twenty-four hour, two hundred mile relay race from Gettysburg to Washington, DC. 100% of the GWS sponsorship dollars goes to support The Hope Connection for Cancer Support.
 
 
 










 
 
 














 
 
 




Hope Connections for Cancer Support
Glassman Wealth Services was awarded the Hope Connections Partnership Award in March 2016 for our support of this incredible organization over the years.
The Hope Connection for Cancer Support helps people affected by cancer enhance their health and well-being through participation in a professional program of emotional support, education and hope. Find out more at at www.hopeconnectionsforcancer.org
 
 
 










 
 
 














 
 
 




Operation First Response
Operation First Response, Inc., supports our nation’s Wounded Heroes and their families with personal and financial needs. Services are provided from the onset of injury, throughout their recovery period and along their journey from military life into the civilian world. To know more, go to www.operationfirstresponse.org.
 
 
 










 
 
 














 
 
 




